---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Game Rules Mastery: Unlock the Secrets to Smart Betting" description="Dive into comprehensive rules for casino classics and sports betting at BetSmart Academy. From blackjack strategies to football odds, master the fundamentals to bet smarter and win bigger in the high-stakes world of gaming.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4B0082] to-[#8A2BE2] py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(255,255,255,0.1)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[length:50px_50px]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block bg-[#FF4500] text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 font-bold text-sm tracking-wider">
          <i class="fas fa-crown mr-2"></i> PRO PLAYER GUIDE
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Game Rules Mastery: 
          <span class="text-[#FF4500]">Unlock the Secrets</span> to Smart Betting
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-[#E0E0E0] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Dive into comprehensive rules for casino classics and sports betting at BetSmart Academy. From blackjack strategies to football odds, master the fundamentals to bet smarter and win bigger in the high-stakes world of gaming.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <button class="bg-[#FF4500] hover:bg-[#ff6333] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
            <i class="fas fa-play-circle mr-2"></i> Start Learning
          </button>
          <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#4B0082] font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-book mr-2"></i> View All Rules
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#f5f5f5]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#4B0082] mb-6">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt text-[#FF4500] mr-3"></i> Game Rules Mastery: Play Like a Pro!
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-[#4B0082] text-white p-6 rounded-xl inline-block">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">
            Welcome to the heart-pounding arena of betting, where knowledge is your ultimate weapon!
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-700 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          At <span class="font-bold text-[#4B0082]">BetSmart Academy</span>, we believe that understanding the rules isn't just smart—it's essential for turning the odds in your favor. Whether you're spinning the roulette wheel, bluffing in poker, or predicting the next touchdown, our guide breaks down the essentials with <span class="font-bold text-[#FF4500]">bold energy</span> and crystal-clear insights. Get ready to level up your game!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Casino Rules Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#4B0082]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-dice text-[#FF4500] mr-3"></i> Casino Game Rules: Hit the Jackpot with Confidence
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#E0E0E0] max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
          Casino floors buzz with excitement, but without rules mastery, you're just another player.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Blackjack Card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#FF4500]">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#FF4500] text-white p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-credit-card text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4B0082]">Blackjack: Beat the Dealer</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Objective</span>: Get a hand value closer to 21 than the dealer without busting.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Key Rules</span>: Split pairs, double down, and take insurance.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Strategy</span>: Use basic strategy charts for optimal play.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full bg-[#4B0082] hover:bg-[#3a0066] text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-book-open mr-2"></i> Master Strategy
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Roulette Card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#FF4500]">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#FF4500] text-white p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-spinner text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4B0082]">Roulette: Spin to Win</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Objective</span>: Predict where the ball will land on the spinning wheel.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Bets</span>: Straight, split, street, corner, and outside bets.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">House Edge</span>: 2.7% for European, 5.26% for American.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full bg-[#4B0082] hover:bg-[#3a0066] text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line mr-2"></i> Analyze Odds
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Poker Card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#FF4500]">
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#FF4500] text-white p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-gamepad text-2xl"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4B0082]">Poker: Outplay Your Opponents</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Objective</span>: Create the best 5-card hand from 7 cards.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Hand Rankings</span>: Royal flush, straight flush, four of a kind.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-2"></i>
                <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Bluffing</span>: Use betting patterns to mislead opponents.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full bg-[#4B0082] hover:bg-[#3a0066] text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-lightbulb mr-2"></i> Learn Bluffing
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sports Betting Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f5f5f5] to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#4B0082] mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-football-ball text-[#FF4500] mr-3"></i> Sports Betting: Predict the Outcome
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
          From football odds to basketball spreads, mastering sports betting rules is crucial for success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 mb-8 border-l-8 border-[#FF4500]">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4B0082] mb-4 flex items-center">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy text-[#FF4500] mr-3"></i> Understanding Betting Lines
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Moneyline</span>: Simple win/loss bet with odds.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Spread</span>: Point differential to level playing field.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Over/Under</span>: Bet on total points scored in a game.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Parlays</span>: Combine multiple bets for higher payouts.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Futures</span>: Long-term wagers on events far in advance.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-[#FF4500] mt-1 mr-3"></i>
                  <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-semibold">Live Betting</span>: Place wagers during games in real-time.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4B0082] to-[#8A2BE2] rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 text-white">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
            <i class="fas fa-star text-[#FF4500] mr-3"></i> Pro Tip: Value Betting
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">
            <span class="font-bold">Value betting</span> is the cornerstone of successful sports betting. It's identifying bets where the probability of winning is higher than what the odds suggest. Always compare bookmaker odds with your own probability assessment.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <button class="bg-[#FF4500] hover:bg-[#ff6333] text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
              <i class="fas fa-calculator mr-2"></i> Calculate Value
            </button>
            <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#4B0082] font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full transition-all duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-circle-info mr-2"></i> Read More
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF4500] to-[#FF6347]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Dominate the Betting Arena?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Join thousands of smart bettors who've already mastered the game rules with BetSmart Academy.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <button class="bg-white text-[#4B0082] hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg text-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket mr-2"></i> Start Free Trial
        </button>
        <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#4B0082] font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 text-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-book-open mr-2"></i> View Full Course
        </button>
      </div>
      <p class="text-white mt-6 opacity-80">
        <i class="fas fa-lock mr-2"></i> 100% Money-back guarantee • No credit card required
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>